"com</email>"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:2783
#, no-c-format
msgid "CREDIT_FOR_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr ""
"<para>Översättning Stefan Asserhäll <email>stefan.asserhall@gmail.com</"
